---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="For Researchers"
  description="Partner with MCLA on MCL research. Learn about collaboration opportunities, research priorities, and how to work with us."
>
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-primary/5 via-warm-white to-sage/20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">For Researchers</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-charcoal/60 leading-relaxed">
        Partnering with the research community to advance MCL science.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
          MCLA is committed to supporting and accelerating research that improves outcomes for MCL patients. We welcome partnerships with researchers and institutions who share our commitment to advancing MCL science.
        </p>

        <h2>How We Support Research</h2>
        <ul class="text-charcoal/70 space-y-3">
          <li><strong>Funding:</strong> As MCLA grows, we plan to offer research grants focused on our priority areas. We are currently building our grants program and welcome expressions of interest.</li>
          <li><strong>Patient engagement:</strong> We can help connect researchers with MCL patients for studies, surveys, and clinical trial recruitment.</li>
          <li><strong>Education and dissemination:</strong> We translate research findings for patient audiences and help increase awareness of important studies and clinical trial opportunities.</li>
          <li><strong>Advocacy:</strong> We advocate for increased federal and private research funding for MCL and for policies that support clinical trial access.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Research Partnership Opportunities</h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/70">We are interested in partnerships that:</p>
        <ul class="text-charcoal/70 space-y-2">
          <li>Address our stated research priorities</li>
          <li>Include patient-reported outcomes and quality of life measures</li>
          <li>Advance understanding of MCL biology and treatment resistance</li>
          <li>Expand access to clinical trials for underserved populations</li>
          <li>Develop educational materials based on the latest evidence</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Clinical Trial Support</h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/70">
          We believe clinical trials are essential for advancing MCL treatment. MCLA can help with trial awareness and patient education, connecting patients with trial opportunities, developing patient-friendly trial information, and advocating for trial design that prioritizes patient experience.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-sage/30 rounded-xl p-6 my-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">Get in Touch</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-4">
            We'd love to hear from researchers interested in collaborating with MCLA. Please contact us to discuss partnership opportunities.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-2.5 bg-teal-primary text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-teal-dark transition-colors no-underline text-sm"
          >
            Contact Our Research Team
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
